{{Top|leg}}
The '''third sector precinct house''' of the [[Office of Peace and Security]] was located on the west side of [[Gadrin]]. Probably the smallest precinct house on [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]], it was a square one-story structure with only one door. It had a small front room with a pair of desks and half a dozen chairs, a holding area, and a supply closet. Hidden behind the supply closet was a stairway which led down to a secret meeting room which had a round table and nine seats. The room was used by the [[Cularin resistance]], and resistance leader [[Gerta Haman]] had OPC agent [[Corporal/Legends|Corporal]] [[Ortin]], secretly also a resistance member, bring a group she was recruiting here to meet with her.

